data.value: Formerly at www.vanessa-mae.us (version 2) and www.vanessa-mae.cc (version 1). The name of this site comes from a proposed title of the upcoming Vanessa-Mae's Biography. This is a fan site only, and I have no connection or contact with Vanessa-Mae or her managers.

Images on this site are copyrighted by EMI Records, Sony, and various individuals. Special thanks to Rijko, Daisy and Arioch for providing scans of programs and compact discs. Other images may have originated at The Red Hot Vanessa-Mae Homepage (www.vanessamae.com).
Version 3 was completed on 04 December, 2017, and is dedication to fans that I believe to have passed on: John R McLemore (CarrollTowerCX), Anna Oei (Daisy Hill), Elisheva Yenny (VMA Storm)
